        The icon is pure, simple, and follows the unbranded style of the
        product. I wanted Currency to blend into the platfrom as if it was a
        bundled utility.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="project-item project-currency-symbols">
      <img
        src="./images/currency-symbols-3x.png"
